net.sourceforge.schemaspy.model

Class Table

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.schemaspy.model.Table
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Table>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RemoteTable, View

    public class Table
extends Object
implements Comparable<Table>
    A Table is one of the basic building blocks of SchemaSpy that knows everything about the database table's metadata.
    Author:
    John Currier

      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(Table other)
        Compare this table to another table. Results are based on 1: identity, 2: table name, 3: schema name

        This implementation was put in place to deal with analyzing multiple schemas that contain identically named tables.
